data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News According to the official announcement, Binance Finance launched a reward activity for dual-currency investment users. Eligible users can enjoy a 26% annualized return bonus and a maximum of 3,000 USDC equivalent rewards.
1. During the event, all new users* who confirm their participation in the event and use BTC, USDT or USDC to subscribe for dual-currency investment will receive a 26% annualized return bonus on top of the minimum 3.65% annualized return at the time of subscription;
2. All new and old dual-currency investment users who confirm their participation in the event will be ranked according to the average BTC, USDT and USDC dual-currency investment subscription volume during the event. The top 50 eligible users can receive a maximum of 3,000 USDC rewards.
